      </div>
     </div>
     <div class="large-feature-inner">
      <div class="content-side">
       <h4>
        Department overview
       </h4>
       <img alt="seven students at an event smiling at the camera" src="images/home-page/alc-home-seven-students-rock-455x255.jpg"/>
       <div class="text">
        <p>
         The Department of Asian Languages and Cultures offers an education in the languages, cultures, and literatures of Asia. Students will acquire linguistic and transcultural competence in one or more regions of Asia and learn to better appreciate Asia as a dynamic site of international cultural relations.
        </p>
        <p class="button">
         <a href="about/department-overview.html">
          Learn More
         </a>
        </p>
       </div>
      </div>
      <div class="right-side">
       <p>
        <strong>
         What we offer:
        </strong>
       </p>
       <ul>
        <li>
         <a href="areas-of-study/index.html">
          Areas of Study
         </a>
        </li>
        <li>
         <a href="undergraduate/majors-minors/index.html">
          Majors and Minors
         </a>
        </li>
        <li>
         <a href="courses/index.html">
          Courses
         </a>
        </li>
        <li>
         <a href="undergraduate/first-year-focus.html">
          First-Year Focus
         </a>
        </li>
        <li>
         <a href="undergraduate/language-placement.html">
          Language Placement
         </a>
        </li>
        <li>
         <a href="undergraduate/study-abroad.html">
          Study Abroad
         </a>
        </li>
       </ul>
      </div>
     </div>
    </section>
